text: kmean tosapei champoh anak tnkhsaaoy ning anak mean chomngu ning anak kmean lotthopheap brichcheak( knong meakra robsa a l laoh)laey brasenbae puokke smaohtrang nung a l laoh ning anakneasar robsa trong noh . kmean hetophl na del trauv bantosa banda anak del sang ampeula laey . haey a l laoh mha aphytosa mha anet sraleanh
